OL,3,C'I couldn't sleep': Victims wait years
OL,4,Cfor justice amid record court backlog
OL,6,FRecord levels of crown court delays
OL,7,Fare deepening the trauma of victims,
OL,8,Fand making many feel justice is "out
OL,9,Fof reach", that's what the Victims
OL,10,FCommissioner has warned, ITV News'
OL,11,FNeil Connery reports
OL,13,FVicki Crawford's fight for justice
OL,14,Fagainst her childhood abuser "broke"
OL,15,Fher, leaving her with a number of
OL,16,Fmental health issues and wanting to
OL,17,Fwithdraw from the whole court process.
