OL,3,C'I couldn't sleep': Victims wait years
OL,4,Cfor justice amid record court backlog
OL,6,FDelays in the Crown Court have reached
OL,7,Frecord levels in England and Wales
OL,8,Fwith 73,105 outstanding cases as of
OL,9,FSeptember 2024 and it is having a
OL,10,Fmajor impact on victims like Ms
OL,11,FCrawford.
OL,13,FShe was groomed and sexually abused by
OL,14,Fan older man when she was 14 but
OL,15,Fdidn't report the crime to police
OL,16,Funtil 2018, more than 30 years later.
