OL,3,C'I couldn't sleep': Victims wait years
OL,4,Cfor justice amid record court backlog
OL,6,F"I didn't really realise what it was
OL,7,Funtil I was 29, when my friend pointed
OL,8,Fout that it wasn't a relationship,
OL,9,Fthat it was childhood sexual abuse,"
OL,10,Fshe said.
OL,12,FHer abuser was charged in 2021.
OL,14,FBut it took five years and eight
OL,15,Fmonths for her case to get to trial
OL,16,Fdue to a number of different delays
OL,17,Fwithin the court system.
