OL,3,C'I couldn't sleep': Victims wait years
OL,4,Cfor justice amid record court backlog
OL,6,F"What made it difficult was being
OL,7,Fbounced around with various court
OL,8,Fdates, so you'd get to the day that
OL,9,Fwas supposed to be the trial and you'd
OL,10,Fget told at 3 or 4 in the afternoon
OL,11,Fthat the trial wasn't going to go
OL,12,Fahead," she said.
OL,14,F"So you'd sit in limbo for that month
OL,15,Fand then the trial date would come
OL,16,Fonly for the same thing to happen
OL,17,Fagain.
