OL,3,C'I couldn't sleep': Victims wait years
OL,4,Cfor justice amid record court backlog
OL,6,F"I ended up with agoraphobia, PTSD, I
OL,7,Fcouldn't sleep at night, I'd have
OL,8,Fnightmares, I'd wake up in the middle
OL,9,Fof panic attacks, I'd have migraine
OL,10,Fafter migraine in the run up to court
OL,11,Fdates.
OL,13,F"Each time it got worse, each time I
OL,14,Ffelt increasingly anxious."
OL,16,FShe said the fifth delay "broke" her
OL,17,Fand she just wanted to withdraw from
OL,18,Fthe whole process.
