OL,3,C'I couldn't sleep': Victims wait years
OL,4,Cfor justice amid record court backlog
OL,6,F"The system itself, the lack of
OL,7,Ffunding, just makes it impossible to
OL,8,Fnavigate as a complainant," Ms
OL,9,FCrawford said.
OL,11,FHer experience with the criminal
OL,12,Fjustice system is far from unique.
OL,14,FThe backlog in the Crown Court has
OL,15,Falmost doubled in five years with
OL,16,Fnearly 50% of victims having their
OL,17,Ftrial adjourned at least once.
