OL,11,FVictims Commissioner Baroness Newlove
OL,12,Ftold ITV News the delays were having
OL,13,Fvery real health impacts on people
OL,14,Faffected by crime.
OL,16,F"The whole strain on their mental
OL,17,Fhealth, their coping mechanisms; they
OL,18,Fwere now turning to alcohol or drugs,
OL,19,Fthey were even self-harming as well
OL,20,Fand sadly some felt suicidal," she
OL,21,Fsaid.
